---
source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: clickbench_q25"
---
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                               |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: hits.SearchPhrase                                                                                                      |
|               |   Sort: to_timestamp(hits.EventTime) ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=10                                                                      |
|               |     Projection: hits.SearchPhrase, hits.EventTime                                                                                  |
|               |       BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                           |
|               |         Filter: CAST(hits.SearchPhrase AS Utf8) != Utf8("")                                                                        |
|               |           TableScan: hits projection=[EventTime, SearchPhrase], partial_filters=[CAST(hits.SearchPhrase AS Utf8) != Utf8("")]      |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[SearchPhrase@0 as SearchPhrase]                                                                              |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[to_timestamp(EventTime@1) ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false]                         |
|               |     CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                         |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase, EventTime@0 as EventTime]                                              |
|               |         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                         |
|               |           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                              |
|               |             FilterExec: CAST(SearchPhrase@1 AS Utf8) !=                                                                            |
|               |               SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                   |
|               |                 RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                              |
|               |                   FallbackOnZeroResultsScanExec                                                                                    |
|               |                     CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                         |
|               |                       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                        |
|               |                         DuckSqlExec sql= SELECT "EventTime", "SearchPhrase" FROM hits WHERE (CAST(SearchPhrase AS VARCHAR) <> '')  |
|               |                                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
